<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Loan Disbursed</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e 0%, #38ef7d 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            margin: -20px -20px 30px -20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .status-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 0 20px 20px 20px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .disbursement-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f7fa 0%, #e8f5e9 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #38ef7d;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #11998e;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .details {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .details .row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .details .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
        }
        .details .value {
            color: #333;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="status-icon">üí∞</div>
            <h1>Loan Disbursed!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{customerName}}</strong>,</p>

            <div class="disbursement-box">
                <p style="margin-top: 0; font-size: 18px;"><strong>Funds Sent Successfully!</strong></p>
                <p>Your loan has been disbursed to your savings account</p>
                <div class="amount">{{amount}} RWF</div>
            </div>

            <h3>Disbursement Details</h3>
            <div class="details">
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Loan Number:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{loanNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Transaction Reference:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{transactionReference}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Credited Account:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{accountNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Disbursed Amount:</span>
                    <span class="value"><strong>{{amount}} RWF</strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">New Balance:</span>
                    <span class="value"><strong>{{newBalance}} RWF</strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Disbursement Date:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{disbursedAt}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="background: #fff3e0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <strong>‚è∞ Payment Reminder:</strong><br>
                Your first repayment of <strong>{{monthlyInstallment}} RWF</strong> is due on <strong>{{firstPaymentDate}}</strong>
            </p>

            <p style="background: #e8f5e9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <strong>üí° Pro Tip:</strong> Set up automatic payments or payment reminders to never miss a due date and keep your credit score healthy!
            </p>

            <p>You can now use these funds for your intended purpose. Remember to make timely repayments to maintain your excellent credit standing.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Credit Jambo Ltd</strong></p>
            <p>Need help? Contact our support team anytime</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
